data.input: I developed a Python project using YOLO with the Ultralytics library to detect buffaloes in images and videos. I trained a custom model on a buffalo dataset and implemented real-time detection. The project outputs bounding boxes and coordinates for each detected buffalo for further analysis or tracking.

I developed a small web development project using React and Node.js. I built a responsive frontend with interactive forms and a backend API for data storage and retrieval. The project allows users to submit, view, and manage information efficiently in a user-friendly interface.
